---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";

const certs = ["CCNA", "CCNP", "GIAC GPEN", "CISSP"];
const arc = [
  { label: "USMC", note: "Voice, internet, and secure internet over microwave equipment." },
  { label: "A.A.S.", note: "Computer Information Science." },
  { label: "Network Engineer", note: "Cisco voice, routing, and switching for critical infrastructure and enterprises." },
  { label: "B.A.S.", note: "Cybersecurity." },
  { label: "M.B.A.", note: "Because the business side matters too." },
  { label: "Consulting", note: "Two decades across critical infrastructure, finance, manufacturing, ICS, academia, and government." },
  { label: "RedSeal", note: "Senior Director — Information Security &amp; Global Professional Services." },
  { label: "Cyberleaf", note: "July 2026 — leading CMMC audits and growing the services practice." },
];
---
<Base title="About" description="Long-form bio: career, certs, and what Nate's up to off the clock.">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 pt-16 pb-20">
    <p class="display-eyebrow mb-4">// ABOUT</p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl">Wonder &amp; wander.</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-[color:var(--color-muted)] italic">Securing the cyber world through clear thinking and innovation.</p>

    <div class="prose-narrow mt-10 space-y-6 text-base md:text-lg">
      <p>
        Nate has been tinkering with computers since he was a kid — the kind of curiosity that turns into a career when you start finding vulnerabilities for fun and getting paid to find them later. After high school he joined the United States Marine Corps, running voice, internet, and secure internet over microwave equipment. From there: an A.A.S. in Computer Information Science, a run as a network engineer wiring up Cisco voice, routing, and switching for critical infrastructure and enterprises, and eventually back to his first love — information security.
      </p>
      <p>
        Along the way he picked up a B.A.S. in cybersecurity, an M.B.A., and certifications including CCNA, CCNP, GIAC GPEN, and CISSP.
      </p>
      <p>
        Today Nate leads global professional services and information security at <span class="text-[color:var(--color-secondary)] font-medium">RedSeal</span>. In July 2026 he steps into CMMC audit leadership at <span class="text-[color:var(--color-secondary)] font-medium">Cyberleaf</span>. Across two decades he has designed, installed, and tested security solutions for critical infrastructure, financial institutions, manufacturing, ICS environments, academia, and government. He's also building <a href="/macropilot" class="font-medium">MacroPilot</a>, a macro-tracking app grounded in real nutrition science.
      </p>
      <p>
        Off the clock, Nate rides motorcycles, sails his 1984 Irwin 43, brews beer, and shares the adventure of life with his wife <span class="font-medium">Dr. Kelly Cash</span>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Certs -->
    <div class="mt-14">
      <p class="display-eyebrow mb-4">// CERTIFICATIONS</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        {certs.map((c) => (
          <span class="rounded-full border border-[color:var(--color-primary)] px-4 py-1.5 text-sm tracking-wide" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">
            {c}
          </span>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Career arc -->
    <div class="mt-14">
      <p class="display-eyebrow mb-6">// THE ARC</p>
      <ol class="space-y-4 border-l-2 border-[color:var(--color-secondary)]/40 pl-6">
        {arc.map((step) => (
          <li>
            <p class="display-eyebrow !text-[color:var(--color-secondary)] !text-xs">// {step.label}</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-relaxed" set:html={step.note}></p>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ol>
    </div>

    <!-- Off the clock -->
    <div class="mt-14">
      <p class="display-eyebrow mb-4">// OFF THE CLOCK</p>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm leading-relaxed">
        <li><span class="text-[color:var(--color-accent)]">⌁</span> Motorcycles. Long roads, foggy mornings, no agenda.</li>
        <li><span class="text-[color:var(--color-accent)]">⌁</span> Sailing the 1984 Irwin 43.</li>
        <li><span class="text-[color:var(--color-accent)]">⌁</span> Soldering iron + curiosity = working PipBoy and a resurrected backup GPS.</li>
        <li><span class="text-[color:var(--color-accent)]">⌁</span> Indiana Jones, Fallout, Zelda. Cosplay incoming.</li>
        <li><span class="text-[color:var(--color-accent)]">⌁</span> Brewing beer. Drinking it. Sharing it.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
